CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper December 29, 1951, pg. 13, reads: "Budding Artist - A Promising Art Student and Her Work... Top right: Peggy and her Chinese 'Pao' prints. In case you haven't gotten to the prints yet, they're in the left-hand corner... - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Peggy Owens (Skillen) wearing mandarin style jacket and seated on ledge with two Chinese prints
